Flag small_base
  Description: Choose the new smaller, split-up base package.

Executable HipmunkPlayground
  if flag(small_base)
    Build-Depends: base >= 3 && < 5, containers >= 0.1 && < 0.4,
                   Hipmunk >= 5.1 && < 5.2, OpenGL >= 2.1 && < 2.3,
                   GLFW >= 0.3 && < 0.4
  else
    Build-Depends: base >= 2 && < 3,
                   Hipmunk >= 5.1 && < 5.2, OpenGL >= 2.1 && < 2.3,
                   GLFW >= 0.3 && < 0.4
  GHC-Options:   -Wall
  Main-is: Playground.hs

